:"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15326,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/23\/sahaba-awe-prophet-sitting\/","url_meta":{"origin":15331,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sitting: Companions in awe of the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Qaylah bint Makhramah reported: I saw the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, sitting with his arms around his legs. When I saw the Messenger of Allah sitting so humbly, I trembled in awe of him. Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4847 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40721,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/07\/way-of-moderation\/","url_meta":{"origin":15331,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Balance: You must take the way of moderation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah al-Aslami reported: I went out one day to fulfill a need, and there was the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, walking before me. The Prophet took my hand, and we set out walking together. A man was praying before us who was performing many bowings and prostrations.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u